routeFacts.name: Peak Forest Railway: Ambergate - Chinley & Buxton
routeFacts.description: Step back in time and discover a long-lost railway, from old-time stations to heavy limestone operations. Re-tread the rails through historical English countryside in the hard-working Fowler 4F. The quaint and waning years of 1960s steam is brought back to life in Train Sim World 3: Peak Forest Railway!
routeInfo: The romantic steam era returns to Train Sim World with the introduction of the iconic Fowler 4F. Built in Derby and dating back to the early 1920s, this prolific fleet of locomotives were designed for mid-ranged freight work by Henry Fowler, Chief Mechanical Engineer of the LMS railway. With 575 produced, but only a handful surviving into preservation, rekindle the flames of this workhorse 0-6-0 tender legend.
